+
+<section class="card accessibility-intro">
+<div>
+<span class="pill">Release 217 · Local accessibility preferences</span>
+<h1 class="section-title" lang="ta">அணுகல்தன்மை மையம்</h1>
+<h2>Accessibility Centre</h2>
+<p>Adjust presentation across pages that load the shared platform bootstrap. Preferences stay in this browser and can be reset at any time.</p>
+</div>
+<div class="accessibility-current">
+<span>Current presentation</span>
+<strong id="accessibilityActive">Default presentation</strong>
+</div>
+</section>
+
+<form id="accessibilityPreferences" class="card" aria-describedby="accessibilityStatus">
+<fieldset>
+<legend><strong>Presentation preferences</strong></legend>
+<div class="accessibility-grid">
+<label class="accessibility-option">
+<input type="checkbox" name="largeText">
+<span><strong>பெரிய எழுத்து · Large text</strong>Increase the base text size and reading line height.</span>
+</label>
+<label class="accessibility-option">
+<input type="checkbox" name="highContrast">
+<span><strong>உயர் மாறுபாடு · High contrast</strong>Use stronger foreground, background and border contrast.</span>
+</label>
+<label class="accessibility-option">
+<input type="checkbox" name="reducedMotion">
+<span><strong>குறைந்த இயக்கம் · Reduced motion</strong>Minimise animation, transitions and smooth scrolling.</span>
+</label>
+<label class="accessibility-option">
+<input type="checkbox" name="underlinedLinks">
+<span><strong>அடிக்கோடிட்ட இணைப்புகள் · Underlined links</strong>Underline ordinary text links so they do not rely on colour alone.</span>
+</label>
+</div>
+</fieldset>
+<div class="accessibility-actions">
+<button class="btn secondary" id="accessibilityReset" type="button">Reset to defaults</button>
+<a class="btn secondary" href="platform.html">Return to Platform Hub</a>
+</div>
+<p id="accessibilityStatus" role="status" aria-live="polite">Loading accessibility preferences…</p>
+</form>
+
+<section class="card accessibility-preview">
+<h2>Reading preview</h2>
+<p lang="ta">வேலும் மயிலும் துணை. இந்த மாதிரி உரை உங்கள் தேர்வுகளை உடனடியாகக் காட்டுகிறது.</p>
+<p>This sample paragraph and <a href="sources.html">ordinary text link</a> update immediately. Buttons remain visually distinct: <a class="btn secondary" href="explore.html">Open Explore</a></p>
+</section>
+
+<section class="card">
+<h2>Scope and limitations</h2>
+<ul>
+<li>Preferences are stored locally and are not synchronized between browsers or devices.</li>
+<li>This centre improves presentation options; it does not claim formal accessibility certification.</li>
+<li>Content accuracy, source status and completeness remain governed by each destination page.</li>
+<li>Browser, operating-system and assistive-technology settings continue to apply independently.</li>
+</ul>
+</section>
+
+<noscript><section class="card" role="status"><h2>JavaScript is disabled</h2><p>The preference controls require JavaScript. Browser zoom, reader mode and operating-system accessibility controls remain available.</p></section></noscript>
+</main>
